room_title: Escape room "The Gridlock" by Escape Reality Puzzle Rooms in Pittsburgh
room_description: In the effort to wake everyone up from the alternate reality referred to as the Grid, you and your team had to return to your ship, the Solomon, to save it from the Seekers. You have just 60 minutes to work together to figure out how to stop them. To successfully complete your task, your group will be faced with a difficult decision.
